values:
Figured it was time for my bi-annual post! Happy turkey day to all you kanuks that might read this... the one time of the year where there is actualy more food then I can eat I love it! Nothing new in my life school sucks, boring as hell which is well normal and nothing new in my life... got new girls in my class to hit on which is always fun and amazing considering the peice of shit hick town that I live in... 

It looks like im going to be STUCK HERE in this peice of shit town because the best university for enginering courses is in the city 30minutes away... fuckin great! I was hoping to get a chance to move somewhere else but nope I get to stay right where I am god damn it! God must be working against me or somthing... oh well I cant be pissed off on a full stomach because food is good!

Somthing ACTUALLY happened in my life, went on a 2 week vacation to victoria (vancouver island in BC canada) was a great trip! A quick summary would be:

Beach, beach, beach, beach, oooohh look at that bikini, beach, beach OH this cool little swimmin hole on a river under a waterfall with friggin ICE COLD damn water, jumped in twice I think I hope I dident shrink anything >.< then theres another beach and my uncle's condo place where I met up with a few girls for like 2 hours, two were alright then this "larger" girl jumped on my back in the swimming pool and tried to steal my sun glasses =( my poor knees, then I hung out with the other two for awhile then drove home 10mins after that which is lame lame lame lame. THEN while driving home some clam my dad picked up which was still closed decided to start ROTTING so I was stuck with this DEAD CLAM crap smell for 3 hours NOT FUN eeww DEAD CLAM.... but all in all vacation was fun!

Even though I doubt anyone even reads this crap... Fill in the blanks with as many words as ya need, then put it in your own LJ o.O please try not to scare me too much...

But as most of you already know the Flames lost the cup final, I havent posted for weeks on end because I am a lazy ass person. Just finished writing all my finals yesterday so school is officialy over for the year! Just gota go tuesday and pick up any awards I might have won and my report card! Weeeeeee!! Let the summer begin, with it's lazy heat and fun filled LAZYNESS!

Last night but someone decided to fuck up my internet around 10:00 and with some reasearch to do for homework tomorow for school as well to do it pissed me off! Fuckin thing just died on me it was fun fun fun! People piss me off... especialy stupid people which is 90% of my town currently watching the Flames game (game one of the stanley cup final) their up 1-zip in the 2nd period would be nice to see them win all this! Im still pissed off at my internet company but I should cheer up if the flames win tonight!
Well not much to say... Flames made the Cup finals! They gona go all the way I can feel it! Went mountain biking other day that was fun as hell umm what else happened.... Not much else to write o.O

Okay what did I doooo... well I watched the Flames move onto round 3! 10,000 people poured onto 17th ave. when the last goal was scored only Calgary can have 10,000 drunk people in one place and have no one get hurt with minimal nudity.


Went to watch Lacross championship... Calgary VS. Buffalo, We won! awsome game real loud nearly a sell out croud... but 10,000 people did not pour onto 17th ave. it was still an awsome game and a great thing to see, Calgary's first lacross championship cup.

Then theres mothers day brunch good food good company and after that spent the day with my mommy =P

What a dumb game! Stupid Red wings they had to win it 2:2 season now now thats just crap! Flames will win next game though... after two goals in 18 seconds which was really NICE they still loose the damn game 4:2 what the hell is that! This is just crap >.<
YEAH after an upsetting loss of 5:2 I think it was against Detroit the Flames return home and win the game! AHA Great game yep and whoever says differently I will personaly kill!
